<plot>Stefos does dangerous stunts with his motorcycle for a living. He is engaged to Roza, a woman who only cares about money and males. One day Stefos meets an executive of a company. This company is buying organs of healthy men, in order to transplant them to wealthy patients. Roza, convinces Stefos to sell most of his organs. Soon he signs a contract with them. The term is that they will be owners of his organs after his death. Stefos is given a huge amount of money and Roza soon spends it in clothing, automobiles and home equipment of various kinds. Afterwards she forces Stefos to sell more of his organs. Now the terms are even more strict. He is not allowed to have sex more than once a week, alcohol is forbidden, and so is smoking. He life is now a nightmare. Roza dumps him for Max, the company's executive. When a wealthy client urgently needs a genital transplant, the company's guys try to kill Stefos. That's when a violent hunt starts.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?405498</url></doc>
